prompts.prompt: Take a photo that represents your current emotion.
Take a photo of yourself pretending to be asleep.
Take a photo that represents your addiction.
Take a photo of the first animal you can find.
Take a photo of the least favorite thing around you.
Take a photo of somebody taking a photo of you.
Take a photo of the smallest thing you can find.
Take a seductive photo with an inanimate object.
Take a photo of the coolest shoes you can find.
Take a photo of a neat pattern.
